Pancake Mix
  --America's Test Kitchen

6 c (30 oz) ap flour
3/4 c (5 1/4 oz) sugar
1/4 c baking powder
1 1/2 tsp baking soda
1 tbsp salt

Combine all ingredients. Can be stored in an airtight container for up to 3 months


To use:
1 batch

3/4 c milk
1 large egg
2 tbsp vegetable oil
1/4 tsp vanilla (optional)
1 c pancake mix

Whisk milk, egg, oil and vanilla in a medium bowl until well combined. Add pancake mix and stir gently with rubber spatula until just combined; batter should look lumpy. Let batter sit for 10 min before cooking.
